Create a Doctor#show page that displays the doctor's name, department, and appointments,
 with each appointment's date, time, and patient name (linking to the patient's show page)

 <%=@doctor.name%>/<%=@doctor.department%><br>
 appointments:
 <% @doctor.appointments.each do |app| %>
 <% @patients = @doctor.patients.find(app.patient_id)%>
 <%= link_to @patients.name, patient_path(@patients)%>-
 <%= link_to app.appointment_datetime.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %k:%M"), appointment_path(app) %>
 <br>
 <%end%>
 